 TV App.\\\\n4. Press on \\\\\\\"Play on TV\\\\\\\" on the mobile app.\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_INSTRUCTIONS_BODY_GENERAL:\\\"\\\\\\\"Play on TV\\\\\\\" lets you launch your favorite movie or TV show directly from your phone to your Smart TV.\\\\n \\\\nYou can use it on any Smart TV where the JustWatch TV App is available or any Roku TV. Just press the \\\\\\\"Play on TV\\\\\\\" button on the mobile app, select your desired device, and then start watching on your TV!\\\\n\\\\nTo get started:\\\\n1. Install the JustWatch TV App on your Smart TV (not for Roku).\\\\n2. Log in to both the JustWatch TV and mobile apps. \\\\n3. Make sure your Google Cast and Roku TV are on or on standby and in the same Wi-Fi as your phone.\\\\n4. If your TV does not have Google Cast, then turn the TV on and launch the JustWatch TV App.\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_INSTRUCTIONS_BODY_GOOGLE_CAST:\\\"\\\\\\\"Play on TV\\\\\\\" lets you launch your favorite movie or TV show directly from your phone to your Google Cast enabled Smart TV. \\\\n\\\\n1. Download and install the JustWatch TV App (version 21.43 or higher) on your Smart TV.\\\\n2. Make sure your Google Cast is on or on standby and in the same Wi-Fi as your phone.\\\\n3. Press \\\\\\\"Play on TV\\\\\\\" on your mobile app.  If no devices are found, press 🔄 to search for them again.\\\\n4. Select your Google Cast device from the list of available devices.\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_INSTRUCTIONS_BODY_ROKU:\\\"\\\\\\\"Play on TV\\\\\\\" lets you launch your favorite movie or TV show directly from your phone to your Roku TV. \\\\n\\\\n1. Make sure your Roku TV is on or on standby and in the same Wi-Fi as your phone.\\\\n2. Press \\\\\\\"Play on TV\\\\\\\" on your mobile app.  If no TVs are found, press 🔄 to search for them again.\\\\n3. Select your Roku TV from the list of available devices. If we don't have the link for the title, then the Roku device is shown, but it is not selectable.\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_INSTRUCTIONS_BODY_WEBSOCKET:\\\"\\\\\\\"Play on TV\\\\\\\" lets you launch your favorite movie or TV show directly from your phone to your Smart TV. \\\\n\\\\n1. Download and install the JustWatch TV App (version 21.43 or higher) on your Smart TV.\\\\n2. Log in to your account on the JustWatch mobile and TV apps.\\\\n3. Press \\\\\\\"Play on TV\\\\\\\" on your mobile app.  If no devices are found, press 🔄 to search for them again.\\\\n4. Turn on your TV and launch the JustWatch TV App.\\\\n5. Select \\\\\\\"JustWatch TV App\\\\\\\" from the list of available devices.\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_INSTRUCTIONS_HEADER:\\\"How to use Play on TV?\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_IT_DID_NOT_WORK:\\\"Did it work?\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_LANDING_PAGE_CFA:\\\"Download the TV App\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_LANDING_PAGE_SUBTITLE:\\\"Once you have installed the JustWatch TV App, follow the instructions on your phone.\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_LANDING_PAGE_TITLE:\\\"Download and install the TV App from the Google Play Store\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_NEW_BUTTON:\\\"Play on TV now\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_NOT_AVAILABLE_DEVICES:\\\"-\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_NOT_AVAILABLE_DEVICES_COPY:\\\"Service is not available on LG TVs at the moment.\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_NO_ROKU:\\\"⛔\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_NO_TVS:\\\"No TVs found.\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_PERMISSION:\\\"We need your permission to discover Cast-enabled devices on your WiFi network\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_POPUP_MOBILE:\\\"Launch your selected movie or TV Show episode directly on your TV with the JustWatch TV App. \\\\n\\\\nYou need to download the JustWatch TV App on any of our supported Smart TVs and Game Consoles and login on both devices. \\\\n\\\\nThen, using your the JustWatch mobile app, just press on the  \\\\\\\"Play on TV \\\\\\\" button and let the magic happen. You just need to grab your own popcorns!\\\\n\\\\nIf you want more detailed instructions, please check the Connect your TV page.\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_POPUP_MOBILE_HEADER:\\\"Play on TV is now available!\\\",WEBAPP_PLAY_ON_TV_SELECT_ROKU:\\\"Selec